---
// Showcase Section - Plain text layout
---

<section id="showcase" class="showcase">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="headline">Problems solved. Apps that work.</h2>
    <p class="intro-text">
      Real discoveries. Real results. Here's how our methodology transforms business challenges into working solutions.
    </p>

    <div class="projects">
      <article class="project">
        <h3>Project Alpha</h3>
        <dl>
          <dt>Challenge</dt>
          <dd>Complex inventory system causing operational delays</dd>
          <dt>Discovery</dt>
          <dd>Real bottleneck was in communication workflow, not the system itself</dd>
          <dt>Result</dt>
          <dd class="result">50% reduction in processing time after addressing the actual problem</dd>
        </dl>
      </article>

      <article class="project">
        <h3>Project Beta</h3>
        <dl>
          <dt>Challenge</dt>
          <dd>Low user adoption of new platform</dd>
          <dt>Discovery</dt>
          <dd>Users needed mobile-first experience for field operations</dd>
          <dt>Result</dt>
          <dd class="result">3x increase in daily active users within 2 months</dd>
        </dl>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .showcase {
    background-color: var(--color-terracotta);
    padding: var(--space-5xl) var(--space-xl);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-width-text);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .headline {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .projects {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .project h3 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .project dl {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
  }

  .project dt {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .project dd {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .project dd.result {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .showcase {
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
    }

    .headline {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }

    .project dl {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xs);
    }

    .project dt {
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }

    .project dt:first-child {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
